      {
         "id": "SECTION_introduction",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>My body has two sides</h3>Place your hands on the table. Do they appear similar? Can you identify any differences between them?</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_hands",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><table class=\"book_navigation\"><tr><td>Left hand</td><td>Right hand</td></tr><tr><td><img id=\"imgLH\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgLH', '0%')\" src=\"images/Left_Hand.png\" class=\"imgcenter\"/></td><td><img id=\"imgRH\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgRH', '0%')\" src=\"images/Right_Hand.png\" class=\"imgcenter\"/></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\">Figure 1: Hands reprsentation. The source codes are available in project GitHub (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('240800f3-ede4-4deb-9d4e-915a3a03fa68'); return false;\">History Tracers Team, <htdate0>, Source code</a>)</td></tr></table></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": [
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2024",
                     "month": "-1",
                     "day": "-1"
                  }
               ],
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "The figure shows a person's two hands raised with all fingers extended, each pointing toward a fruit.",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p>Now, bring your hands together with palms facing and examine your fingers. Do they possess identical sizes? What about your hands—are they also of the same size?</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_draw_hands",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Drawing</h3>Fold a piece of paper in half. Place your left hand on one side and trace its outline with a pencil. Once completed, repeat the process with your right hand on the other side. <table class=\"draw\"><tr><td>Left hand</td><td>Right hand</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/White.png\" class=\"imgcenter\"/></td><td><img src=\"images/White.png\" class=\"imgcenter\"/></td></tr></table></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_body",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>My body</h3>Next, take a look at your arms. Do they exhibit similar features? How about your legs? Can you observe they are equl, where one side of your body mirrors the other? Compare with your friend or teacher to see if they also have equal sides.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_conclusion",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Conclusion and practice</h3>Our bodies are unique, with symmetrical sides. And we're not alone—many other organisms exhibit similar symmetry. Explore leaves of plants and observe other animals to confirm their symmetrical features.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      }
